{"tid":354701,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"「玩命吸輻射」毒遊烏克蘭11天，有咩要注意？","createTime":"2017-08-10T16:18:39.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-05T10:31:59.000Z","uid":128996,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"75449d5f0eff384fa430cd59eecb47f08d3986f4","tid":354701,"uid":128996,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-10T16:18:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">講明先！旅行途中不定期更新！求你地推下POST好啦唔好怒屌</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n是咁的，細佬一直都好想去烏克蘭遊下，去睇下靚女睇下核電廠。咁岩又比我請到兩個禮拜大假，所以諗都唔諗就買機票去馬了。<br />\n<br />\n呢次都係細佬第一次獨遊，仲要係第一次去歐洲，所以想係到記錄一下。理論上應該會一路玩一路更新，如果唔係我都只可以講聲唔好意思了。。。<br />\n<br />\n本次旅程就由 8號去到18號，主要去兩個大城市，基輔同利維夫。當然去得烏克蘭梗係會去獨立廣場同切爾諾貝爾呢個重大景點啦，細佬係香港都係一個廢墟撚黎，香港好多廢墟都去過下。咁梗係想去睇下<br />\n發生史上最嚴重核事故既遺址。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">行程</span><br />\n<br />\n8號 Kyiv&mdash;&gt;(9-12號) Lviv&mdash;&gt;(13-18號)Kyiv<br />\n（來往Kyiv同Lviv都係搭通宵火車）（13-14 2Days Tour）<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">事前準備</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">錢</span><br />\n<br />\n問左朋友話美金最好用，所以我都聽佢話唱美金去<br />\n係香港唱錢我建議去重興大廈入面間堅成<br />\n之前唱過日元都係揀佢<br />\nRATE唔錯又方便（我係尖沙咀返工）<br />\n<br />\n同埋去到當地其實周街都有找換店<br />\n好多大路歐洲貨幣都有得唱<br />\n好多連日元都有得唱<br />\n<br />\n100HKD=328.28UAH<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">機票</span><br />\n<br />\n上網見到機票最短時間最平都係土耳其航空，8000有找來回都係14個鐘左右，但係我就想豪少少，見到有阿聯酋A380加FLYDUBAI 737（杜拜廉航）都係8500到，又未坐過A380所以就揀佢了。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">簽證</span><br />\n<br />\n有特衰既免簽14日，唔洗搞簽證。成個大中華區好似得台灣要搞簽證。<br />\n<br />\n過關個陣佢會問你黎既目的，話係旅行就OK，跟住行多兩步到海關個陣又有人會問你帶左幾多CASH黎，我今次帶左1300 USD去。佢聽到諗都唔諗就放行了。<br />\n<br />\n過完基輔機場個關<br />\n<img src=\"http://i44.photobucket.com/albums/f12/hkgchernobyl/IMG_5621_zpssgfit16h.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi44.photobucket.com%2Falbums%2Ff12%2Fhkgchernobyl%2FIMG_5621_zpssgfit16h.jpg&h=5801afb2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n待續"},{"pid":"6ab786f53af2481e53f862ab5b4525eaab3f003f","tid":354701,"uid":66147,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-10T16:24:02.000Z","msg":"Lm睇烏克蘭妹<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bf41ad48028cac70cf4a44321f81bddedc706e02","tid":354701,"uid":4237,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-10T16:24:47.000Z","msg":"注意輻射"},{"pid":"35adb5948d38cfec0fca15b848a73e2c457c8a6a","tid":354701,"uid":66954,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-10T16:30:05.000Z","msg":"上年去物價平到痴線 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唔知宜家烏紙升返未呢?"},{"pid":"ce52ed53a483d2a1f173e550f73ed447e9f08805","tid":354701,"uid":117777,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-10T16:45:10.000Z","msg":"小心幅射<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/31.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"29ca448f729af1fc86a9fca59670ce9946f18323","tid":354701,"uid":76216,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-10T16:46:19.000Z","msg":"辦好身後事未"},{"pid":"7286a271bf2597285119a4cc6c9c0a7ce1c0282c","tid":354701,"uid":128996,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-10T17:29:40.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>上年去物價平到痴線 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唔知宜家烏紙升返未呢?</blockquote><br />\n依加都仲係好平<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"59febdeb01da8334703bea1544b9b8ab0f758572","tid":354701,"uid":46454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-10T23:56:52.000Z","msg":"而家係烏克蘭輻射唔係最危險,班俄佬先係最危險,唔知幾時又再打過 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5549843feb619f52a7990d39f781e109b672b8dc","tid":354701,"uid":33896,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-11T00:04:24.000Z","msg":"影多幾張靚女相番黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bd5ff07690d3a47ca007a819d542feceee6f92e8","tid":354701,"uid":36157,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-11T02:42:46.000Z","msg":"正皮以示支持"},{"pid":"6ea777e93a7b01106888641204b76f1a420cdb21","tid":354701,"uid":128996,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-11T05:34:06.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>而家係烏克蘭輻射唔係最危險,班俄佬先係最危險,唔知幾時又再打過 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我個fd仲叫我一定要去克里米亞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1d2f04fddec5d1041b91118fbf5a713e0eeb75c7","tid":354701,"uid":37661,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-11T05:50:18.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>而家係烏克蘭輻射唔係最危險,班俄佬先係最危險,唔知幾時又再打過 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我個fd仲叫我一定要去克里米亞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n克里米亞先安全<br />\n<br />\n不過烏克蘭你都通唔到落克里米亞<br />\n<br />\n要兜番去俄羅斯先可以再落去"},{"pid":"5cf55538a73e934f39594d32488d488c3ddf99d5","tid":354701,"uid":128996,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-11T06:20:54.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>而家係烏克蘭輻射唔係最危險,班俄佬先係最危險,唔知幾時又再打過 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我個fd仲叫我一定要去克里米亞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n克里米亞先安全<br />\n<br />\n不過烏克蘭你都通唔到落克里米亞<br />\n<br />\n要兜番去俄羅斯先可以再落去</blockquote><br />\n係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n唔通上返去又搭飛機落去咩"},{"pid":"a6d614c639eabc5911747c3b2476154d29016226","tid":354701,"uid":3688,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-11T06:25:38.000Z","msg":"有冇巴打相認<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6e7e482af97927835af7bd7fd228c0c6f90b051d","tid":354701,"uid":36543,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-11T06:32:47.000Z","msg":"留名"},{"pid":"80382a8daba01c94c5e92bb03aba3b2f92c7096d","tid":354701,"uid":27008,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-11T06:47:39.000Z","msg":"留個名先  利申係土耳其等緊搭飛機去基輔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1211dfaf29cca875017e880b612b374ede8813e9","tid":354701,"uid":128996,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-11T07:20:17.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>留個名先  利申係土耳其等緊搭飛機去基輔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 你估下我地有冇可能係入面相認"},{"pid":"da7283f26136e8d9d4aab5c8dfef09e0d1cf98ba","tid":354701,"uid":19421,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-11T07:22:27.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"7ff01a7a9d41a35969f948fa603ae21afba57299","tid":354701,"uid":128996,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-11T07:23:41.000Z","msg":"今晚再update多一篇<br />\n<br />\n食個早餐先<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/08/11/152338_955c5db21afdb96029b2f76462f58631.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F08%2F11%2F152338_955c5db21afdb96029b2f76462f58631.jpg&h=165682db&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"eb26d0c4f0f10f8556c2572ea6d632f5a0678a7b","tid":354701,"uid":34542,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-11T07:25:13.000Z","msg":"女呢，孝子"},{"pid":"c7bbd48bc87f2a768e0dc797f848145469ac4f0f","tid":354701,"uid":60817,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-11T07:36:47.000Z","msg":"個邊有咩玩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9ce60d58b064e85cc9ff0f6e16f632b0354d95e4","tid":354701,"uid":128996,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-11T07:42:33.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>女呢，孝子</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/08/11/154205_64c5233201a7e99a56605e078c3991c8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F08%2F11%2F154205_64c5233201a7e99a56605e078c3991c8.jpg&h=20556e35&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/08/11/154211_ee9c80248fd22df2aed2ca4a5cc8b1c6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F08%2F11%2F154211_ee9c80248fd22df2aed2ca4a5cc8b1c6.jpg&h=04a23253&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/08/11/154215_9b3ac0b9f822dfbddd02bd5f0fc24320.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F08%2F11%2F154215_9b3ac0b9f822dfbddd02bd5f0fc24320.jpg&h=3a5ad3a4&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/08/11/154220_1c4c9fb33a758a5c848f30c3c7b22064.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F08%2F11%2F154220_1c4c9fb33a758a5c848f30c3c7b22064.jpg&h=9a99fdf0&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/08/11/154227_a1eea60b8892741ce9e2a1a0f76f35b7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F08%2F11%2F154227_a1eea60b8892741ce9e2a1a0f76f35b7.jpg&h=ebdea653&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"61400f626439ee4c112185367cf9e5363d313e41","tid":354701,"uid":128996,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-11T07:42:42.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>女呢，孝子</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/08/11/154205_64c5233201a7e99a56605e078c3991c8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F08%2F11%2F154205_64c5233201a7e99a56605e078c3991c8.jpg&h=20556e35&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/08/11/154211_ee9c80248fd22df2aed2ca4a5cc8b1c6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F08%2F11%2F154211_ee9c80248fd22df2aed2ca4a5cc8b1c6.jpg&h=04a23253&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/08/11/154215_9b3ac0b9f822dfbddd02bd5f0fc24320.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F08%2F11%2F154215_9b3ac0b9f822dfbddd02bd5f0fc24320.jpg&h=3a5ad3a4&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/08/11/154220_1c4c9fb33a758a5c848f30c3c7b22064.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F08%2F11%2F154220_1c4c9fb33a758a5c848f30c3c7b22064.jpg&h=9a99fdf0&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/08/11/154227_a1eea60b8892741ce9e2a1a0f76f35b7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F08%2F11%2F154227_a1eea60b8892741ce9e2a1a0f76f35b7.jpg&h=ebdea653&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"c04d64d9b76fffefa82f2e029df1134ce2fbed61","tid":354701,"uid":54812,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-11T07:52:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"31aebb5fbb8df7f74ca70acb94d0a7618cb4c9f9","tid":354701,"uid":74142,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-12T12:08:44.000Z","msg":"上個冬天獨遊基輔五日，加Chernobyl Tour, 遲下grad trip 去烏克蘭東部Karkov Odessa Dnipro 切爾諾夫策。你十一日淨係去咁少地方值咩？"}]}